data.description: Amazing 3 bed/2 bath modular home seated on the hill of a gorgeous .62 acre lot with large oak trees and a producing citrus tree. Home features open floor plan with lots of windows for natural light. Kitchen is spacious with solid surface countertops and island, family room has wood floors and gas fireplace with remote. Home has large covered front porch with 2 porch swings and a screened back porch offering plenty of space to relax and enjoy the views of the beautiful yard. Large carport and 16'x24' workshop.
